<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM4.2.7">
<l>uḷaiya voṇṭiṟal poṉpeya rōṉtaṉa turampiḷan tutirattai</l>
<l>yaḷaiyum veñciṉat taripari kīṟiya vappaṉvan tuṟaikōyil</l>
<l>iḷaiya maṅkaiya riṇaiyaṭic cilampiṉō ṭeḻilkoḷpan taṭippōrkai</l>
<l>vaḷaiyil niṉṟoli malkiya nāṅkūr vaṇpuru ṭōttamamē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The temple where dwells the father who, having arrived [incarnate],</l>
<l rend="indent">split the horse,</l>
<l>The fiery, raging lion which, having split the chest of the strong, able one</l>
<l rend="indent">whose name was Gold,</l>
<l>Twisted  its claws so that he died, is Vaṉpuruṭōttamam in Nānkūr</l>
<l rend="indent">where abounds</l>
<l>The tinkling from bangles on the arms of those who hit a colorful ball</l>
<l rend="indent">and from ankle bells on both feet of little girls.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
